headline: ? How One Investor Is Profiting From Consumers’ Love of Travel
summary: In the latest WSJ’s Take On the Week podcast, I speak with Eric Resnick, CEO of KSL Capital Partners, about the resilience of the travel sector. He sees leisure travel demand as an anchor that allows the industry to defy pressures typically seen in an economic downturn.
